Title: The League of the Matahari
Plot: Spy handler Frank is honoured and totally bowled over when he's invited to join a top secret order, the League of Mata Hari. But our curious spies can't help but probe and their meddling leads them to a criminal conspiracy deep within MI9 that includes top brass! Our team risk their careers and their lives to lead the purge of the traitors...
